<i>Posted by Giland on 10-26-2001 08:21 PM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p>Generally BeZoie, if someone is multiquesting with you, you pay them first, then they MQ with you.<br />
Multiquesting is where you need something for a quest that is nodrop and someone else has it. They turn in thier part, then you turn in yours and you get the reward as if you turned in both parts. The NPC doesn't know they came from two different chars.<FONT face="arial, helvetica" size="2"><br>
__________________<br>
Giland Bladedancer<br />
ECI</font></p>
