No offense intended to you at all, but I hate that kind of cop-out.  Roleplay or not, people can't just go around screwing other players over.  There are ways to roleplay an evil character or a thief without hurting other people.  In general society, stealing is unacceptable.  The same rules need to apply in all facets of society, including EQ.<br />
<br />
